1 Sec. 2. 18 V.S.A. § 1794 is added to read:
2 § 1794. INFANT CHANGING STATIONS
3 (a) At least one restroom in any public building or place of public
4 accommodation shall contain an infant changing station and the restroom shall
5 be available for use by any individual, regardless of gender.
6 (b) The Commissioner of Public Safety may inspect for compliance under
7 subsection (a) of this section during any inspection conducted pursuant to
8 20 V.S.A. § 2731(b).
9 Sec. 3. EFFECTIVE DATE
10 This act shall take effect on July 1, 2025.
